International Land Alliance, Inc. Key Developments

International Land Alliance, Inc. Announces to Open New Property
May 4 16
International Land Alliance, Inc. announced the company’s official groundbreaking at its property, Oasis Park Resort. International Land Alliance has partnered with Constructora Arizona de México, S.A. De C.V. to begin construction on the Oasis Park Resort, a 497-acre beachfront development in San Felipe, Baja California, México.


