International Land Alliance is a land investment firm based in San Diego, California. ILA’s primary goal is to sell desirable properties at competitive prices with favorable financing options for individual and/or multiple lot purchases for all types of investors and buyers. International Land Alliance inventory includes residential, commercial, recreational, waterfront, ranch, and other types of… · More properties. ILA offers guaranteed-acceptance financing for every client. With the middle-man removed from the process, loans are approved directly by the Company. ILA-Direct loans feature no pre-payment penalties, no credit or background checks, and below-market interest rates.






