Oasis Park Resort
 






 

“The Gateway to the Sea of Cortez”
San Felipe – Puertecitos Corridor
Northern Baja California, Mexico
Own your own private oasis from the majestic mountains in the back, to the beautiful Sea of Cortez up front. The views from these lots are magical. This area deserves to be yours to make your dreams of beachfront living come true for your family and friends. The property values here are soon to go up quickly, now that the first section of the Coastal Highway has been finished in addition to the many other projects planned for the San Felipe-Puertecitos corridor. The Coastal highway gives direct access to the resort making road travel from the US an easy  2 1/2 hour drive. The elevations and the awe inspiring views on this particular property is a must see. This is the Lifestyle you have always dreamed of…
Oasis Park Resort is a 497 acre master planned real estate community just south of San Felipe that offers breathtaking 180-degree sea and mountain views from every home site. Oasis Park Resort is being developed as an ecotourism, green community to coincide with the unique, breath-taking natural amenities that only Baja California provides.





 
There are 1,344 residential home sites which are approximately 1/4-acre each. Your choice of dream lots start as low as $35,000.00. In addition to the residential lots, there will be an RV park with full hook-ups, a boutique hotel, a spacious commercial center, and a nautical center with boat launch and fishing marina, as well as many other exclusive amenities currently not available in nearby developments. Did we mention the VIEWS, the ocean views, the mountain views and the sky views – which makes for the most incredible star gazing around. Add to that lots of clean air, unspoiled terrain and excellent year round climate – we call that paradise!
Once you are here in San Felipe, the Gateway to the Sea of Cortez…. you know your dream has come true!

 
 
 
 

 

